22:32.811 --> 22:34.562
Doing good. Here.

22:34.646 --> 22:36.022
Do one of these on your chin.

22:36.106 --> 22:37.524
Go sideways to your chin.

22:37.607 --> 22:40.235
KATE:
Guys, come on,
pin the tail on the donkey!

22:40.318 --> 22:42.904
