to do all this?

22:42.987 --> 22:45.448
I don't know,
it's all baby stuff anyways.

22:45.532 --> 22:47.450
I know, right, I mean...
(chuckles)

22:47.534 --> 22:49.452
-we're shaving.
-(chuckles)

22:49.536 --> 22:52.747
Hey, don't underestimate
your sister, gentlemen.

22:52.831 --> 22:54.582
She gets it.

22:54.666 --> 22:57.252
