what we're doing, just...

23:16.646 --> 23:19.816
collecting these little moments.

23:20.859 --> 23:23.194
We don't recognize them
when we're in 'em because...

23:23.278 --> 23:26.072
well, we're too busy
looking forward.

23:27.574 --> 23:30.035
But then we spend
the rest of our lives

23:30.118 --> 23:32.120
looking back.

23:33.913 --> 23:35.915
Trying to,
trying to remember them.

23:37.792 --> 23:40.003
Trying to be back inside 'em.

23:43.631 --> 23:46.301
Hmm, it's strange,
the things you remember.

23:46.384 --> 23:48.678
KEVIN:
You're being really weird, Dad.

23:48.762 --> 23:51.639
Mm-hmm, really weird.

23:51.723 --> 23:53.725
