23:55.727 --> 23:57.687
All right, looking good.

23:57.771 --> 23:59.773
Hold on, hold on,
let me have a look at you.

24:03.026 --> 24:06.237
-Yep, still my sons.
-(both laugh)

24:20.460 --> 24:23.713
Just checking in on you.

24:25.674 --> 24:26.591
(sniffles)

24:26.675 --> 24:28.176
Barely slept.

24:28.259 --> 24:30.595
I was up all night
writing a eulogy,

24:30.679 --> 24:33.056
and I can't remember
a single thing that I said.

24:38.853 --> 24:42.023
A depressing notion
for a depressing day-- may I?

24:46.569 --> 24:48.988
It all just feels so...

24:49.072 --> 24:50.907
pointless.

24:52.283 --> 24:55.912
I spent my entire childhood
worrying about losing her.

24:55.995 --> 24:58.498
I spent the past decade

24:58.581 --> 25:00.917
abjectly terrified of it.

25:02.794 --> 25:04.796
And now she's gone.

25:06.047 --> 25:08.216
And yet...

25:08.299 --> 25:10.885
the birds chirp on.

25:12.721 --> 25:14.723
I notice that I'm hungry.

25:16.182 --> 25:18.768
Five minutes ago,
I thought about work.

25:18.852 --> 25:21.146
Tomorrow I'll shower.

25:23.189 --> 25:26.026
It just all feels so pointless.

25:30.739 --> 25:32.741
That too depressing?

25:32.824 --> 25:35.452
Definitely less funny
than your eulogy.

25:35.535 --> 25:37.078
(laughs)

25:41.374 --> 25:42.542
(sniffles)

25:42.625 --> 25:45.170
