while I'm gone, do you hear?

26:39.766 --> 26:42.227
-Okay.
-Okay, then.

26:42.310 --> 26:45.146
Go back to sleep.

27:02.080 --> 27:03.998
(exhales)

27:04.082 --> 27:06.042
Grandfather.

27:06.126 --> 27:08.044
Strange word.

27:08.128 --> 27:09.838
Grand. Father.

27:09.921 --> 27:11.423
(exhales)

27:11.506 --> 27:13.508
Never thought of myself
as either, really.

27:13.591 --> 27:15.802
-Well, look at you now.
-Well...

27:15.885 --> 27:17.387
look at me now.

27:19.973 --> 27:22.809
Such a strange relationship:
grandparent.

27:22.892 --> 27:26.146
Not as complicated as parent,
not as fraught.

27:26.229 --> 27:28.398
But it's just...

27:28.481 --> 27:30.483
unconditional.

27:30.567 --> 27:33.194
Easy, pure love.

27:33.278 --> 27:36.322
What an unusual thing.

27:36.406 --> 27:38.783
To love someone
so unconditionally

27:38.867 --> 27:41.494
when you know time
probably won't allow you

27:41.578 --> 27:43.580
to be a big part of their story.

27:48.835 --> 27:50.837
I don't remember
my grandparents.

27:52.589 --> 27:55.508
I can only access
fleeting images.

27:55.592 --> 27:58.219
Smells.

27:58.303 --> 28:00.972
The smell of pies.

28:01.056 --> 28:03.725
She made pies, I think,
my mother's mother.

28:05.935 --> 28:07.687
My father's father
smoked a pipe.

28:07.771 --> 28:10.398
I remember
the smell of that pipe.

28:13.151 --> 28:16.571
Oh, I look
at those two little girls.

28:18.156 --> 28:20.575
I've known them
all of seven months,

28:20.658 --> 28:23.495
and only now
can I even comprehend

28:23.578 --> 28:27.332
how intensely my grandparents
must have loved me.

28:28.875 --> 28:31.920
And all I can remember
are fleeting images.

28:32.003 --> 28:34.923
Smells of pies and pipes.

28:38.593 --> 28:41.471
I wonder what
they'll remember about me.

28:42.555 --> 28:43.723
A lot.

28:43.807 --> 28:46.184
Yeah, a selfish thing
to worry about,

28:46.267 --> 28:48.812
-I know...
-A lot.

28:52.440 --> 28:55.777
Plus you got that really nice,
really distinctive smell.

28:55.860 --> 28:57.696
Well, thank God for that.

28:57.779 --> 29:00.281
